<p><lb/>Item aber sol er die <persName ref="per013787">Felix Maness</persName><note><persName ref="per013787">Felix Manesse</persName> war Baumeister der Stadt <placeName ref="loc000065">Zürich</placeName>
(im Amt 1407-1424, vgl. <bibl><ref target="http://permalink.snl.ch/bib/chbsg000030960">HLS</ref>, <ref target="https://hls-dhs-dss.ch/de/articles/018089">Felix Manesse</ref></bibl>).</note>
verbuwen hat <measure type="currency" unit="lb" quantity="25">xxv </measure>.
</p></seg>
